A SINGLE SUPPLIER, WE ARE UNDER NO OBLIGATION TO EXCLUSIVELY SOURCE COMPONENTS FROM THESE VENDORS IN THE FUTURE. BEYOND THE EXCEPTIONS NOTED, WE GENERALLY HAVE THE

