WORLDWIDE MACROECONOMIC FACTORS HAVE A STRONG

CORRELATION TO BUSINESS AND CONSUMER DEMAND FOR OUR SOFTWARE, SERVICES, GAMES AND INTERNET SERVICE OFFERINGS. WE EXPECT A BROAD CONTINUATION IN THE ECONOMIC CONDITIONS AND DEMAND IN FISCAL YEAR 2007 AS COMPARED TO FISCAL YEAR 2006.

AS OPEN SOURCE SOFTWARE DEVELOPMENT AND DISTRIBUTION EVOLVES, WE CONTINUE TO SEEK TO DIFFERENTIATE OUR PRODUCTS FROM COMPETING PRODUCTS THAT ARE BASED ON OPEN

SOURCE SOFTWARE. WE BELIEVE THAT MICROSOFTS SHARE OF SERVER UNIT OPERATING SYSTEMS INCREASED IN FISCAL YEAR 2006.

