AND ONENOTE. REVENUE GROWTH DEPENDS ON THE ABILITY TO ADD VALUE TO THE CORE OFFICE PRODUCT SET AND EXPAND OUR PRODUCT OFFERINGS IN OTHER INFORMATION WORKER AREAS SUCH AS ENTERPRISE CONTENT MANAGEMENT, COLLABORATION, UNIFIED COMMUNICATIONS, AND

