IS DERIVED PRIMARILY FROM ADVERTISERS ON MSN, FROM CONSUMERS AND PARTNERS THROUGH SUBSCRIPTIONS AND TRANSACTIONS GENERATED FROM ONLINE PAID SERVICES, AND FROM MSN NARROWBAND INTERNET ACCESS SUBSCRIBERS. IN FISCAL YEAR 2006, WE LAUNCHED MSN ADCENTER

