SUBSCRIPTIONS, AND OTHER AGREEMENTS WHERE MICROSOFT IS COMMITTED TO THE DELIVERY OF FUTURE ENHANCEMENTS, PRODUCTS, OR SERVICES, INCLUDING THE TV PLATFORM.

